        "creation_date": 1595228611,
        "body": "<p>PFB code based on the approach suggested by @Alec:<\/p>\n<pre><code>    public static void main(String[] args) throws Exception {\n        ActorSystem system = ActorSystem.create();\n        SourceQueueWithComplete&lt;Pair&lt;Integer, String&gt;&gt; sq = Source.&lt;Pair&lt;Integer, String&gt;&gt;queue(10, OverflowStrategy.backpressure())\n                .asSourceWithContext(Pair::second)\n                .map(Pair::first)\n                .to(Sink.foreach(param -&gt; CompletableFuture.completedFuture(param).thenAccept(System.out::println)))\n                .run(system);\n        // Pushing elements in the SourceQueue (sq) created above\n        List&lt;Pair&lt;Integer, String&gt;&gt; list = List.of(Pair.create(1, &quot;one&quot;), Pair.create(2, &quot;two&quot;));\n        list.forEach(pair -&gt; sq.offer(pair));\n    }\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
